{"tid":733764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英格蘭28年來首晉4強　倫敦球迷宜家大肆搗亂","createTime":"2018-07-08T05:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T14:13:42.000Z","uid":182315,"like":9,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8d963181f4e9d205bbcdee418b481524075b70","tid":733764,"uid":182315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"英格蘭昨晚在俄羅斯世界盃8強，憑上、下半場各入一個頭槌，以2：0輕取瑞典，是繼1990年以來，再次晉身世界盃準決賽。在倫敦，不少「三獅軍團」球迷在街頭瘋狂慶祝，甚至有人闖入瑞典品牌宜家家居分店大肆搗亂，惹起熱議。遭殃的宜家分店位於東倫敦的史特拉福區。網傳片段所見，球迷們在宜家內揮舞着英格蘭旗，大唱打氣歌曲，甚至在展覽區內的牀褥跳躍。周邊的工作人員無可奈何，唯有站在一旁觀察。當地傳媒曾向宜家查詢，未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n此外，瑞典駐英國大使索爾斯特羅姆（Torbjorn Sohlstrom）亦在twitter發帖，祝賀英格蘭晉級4強，稱讚英軍門將比克福特表現出色，又笑言自己會在消化賽果後，支持英格蘭奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭4強賽事將對陣克羅地亞，會於本港時間周四（12日）凌晨2時展開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180708/s00006/1531010751577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180708%2Fs00006%2F1531010751577&d=4I0nUGy1hPUuHKx6tC%2BvADPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f5c96389\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180708%2Fs00006%2F1531010751577&h=6aaa1323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180708/s00006/1531010751577</a>"},{"pid":"851ae376009a86dfbecd5fb7e91f4cf2f7a5144c","tid":733764,"uid":131323,"like":188,"dislike":5,"score":183,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同嬴國一鳩樣"},{"pid":"f49fd9ee5aa7145f8936871aa576ad9edfcac761","tid":733764,"uid":71913,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:12:06.000Z","msg":"發神經"},{"pid":"d0d8c9bccf4e9bce483d223b1f11b6de6291dc73","tid":733764,"uid":132587,"like":226,"dislike":36,"score":190,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"好想克羅地亞收英撚皮<br />\n踢到咁垃圾仲可以咁串柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla