可奈何，唯有站在一旁觀察。當地傳媒曾向宜家查詢，未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n此外，瑞典駐英國大使索爾斯特羅姆（Torbjorn Sohlstrom）亦在twitter發帖，祝賀英格蘭晉級4強，稱讚英軍門將比克福特表現出色，又笑言自己會在消化賽果後，支持英格蘭奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭4強賽事將對陣克羅地亞，會於本港時間周四（12日）凌晨2時展開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180708/s00006/1531010751577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180708%2Fs00006%2F1531010751577&d=4I0nUGy1hPUuHKx6tC%2BvADPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f5c96389\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180708%2Fs00006%2F1531010751577&h=6aaa1323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180708/s00006/1531010751577</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:19:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至有人闖入瑞典品牌宜家家居分店大肆搗亂，惹起熱議。</span><br />\n垃圾人種不分國界"},{"pid":"eeedc62de556223e30bdebde7571b909db8fa873","tid":733764,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"East London<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出左名雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f3db4f24ab171205eaa6d9621c0ec8b1ea75e2","tid":733764,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"17418034c0dc40265f09708cc2964c2b514ec763","tid":733764,"uid":41658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a4eaa44ede83af74b4df054d68c67351a0ebbe74","tid":733764,"uid":77731,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"東倫敦不嬲都係低下地區<br />\n正如天水圍深水埗黃大仙咁<br />\n住滿劣質廢人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"南倫敦仲差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:24:44.000Z","msg":"其實London住得人嘅得west London <br />\n唔少londoner 搬左去周邊d郡<img